Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:13.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底知れぬ深い海でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:19.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　波を蹴って虹架けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:25.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　今じゃなくちゃ出来ないから!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.25,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうでもないような日常でバッタリ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間的な闘争本能ではったり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:36.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船飛んで来て銀河外交…なんてね!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほっぺた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（つねっても）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛い…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:42.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（夢じゃない）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:47.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現実のほうがかなりスリル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退屈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（したくない）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:53.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（夢を見よ）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗でも主役級　ド迫力だい!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:04.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空に疾風　吹かせてみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:10.54,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青い自転車きしませて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.21,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あざ笑う急勾配に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:21.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　傷つく勇気　見つける旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:27.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　急かす今と走り出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:13.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是深不可測的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:19.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　也要衝破風浪越過彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:25.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　因為只有現在才能做到!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在無聊的平日裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用瞬間的鬥爭本能虛張聲勢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:36.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和飛來的宇宙船做銀河外交…怎麼可能呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉頰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（掐一下）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:42.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（不是夢）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:47.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界相當刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:50.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（不想那樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:53.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（去做夢吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失敗也是主角級的超級氣魄!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:04.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中卷起旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:10.54,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅動藍色的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑那陡坡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:21.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}earnest dive　每當發現受傷的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:27.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}bustling day　與匆忙的現在一起出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:33.24,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　追い風を追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:40.93,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしなく　過去から未来まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.78,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミを守る！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:57.55,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life　コラボレーション
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:01.39,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミとボクはメビウスのコンビネーション
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.39,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love　運命事情↓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:08.92,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複雑→心拍数上昇↑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:13.98,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失うことが怖いんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:19.68,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あきらめたりしたくないそれだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:24.41,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミとの約束があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:27.54,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:34.71,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠久で見たようなめぐり逢い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.62,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神のミステイク？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:42.45,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　向かい風向かってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:50.10,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しいStageを目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.63,OPJ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}キミと行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:33.24,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　乘著風追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:40.93,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有終點　從過去到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.78,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠守護著你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:57.55,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life　共同協作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:01.39,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你與我有著無限的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.39,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love　因為命運↓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:08.92,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複雜→心跳加快↑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:13.98,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:19.68,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:24.41,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和你有所約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:27.54,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:34.71,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠久而似曾相識的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.62,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的失誤？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:42.45,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Wind　迎著風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:50.10,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著新的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.63,OPC1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}與你一同邁進！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像最終回一樣在完美的氛圍中落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後接上一集的第二天早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是打了一天工  然後參加了一下咲夜小姐的生日聚會就倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不做做運動鍛煉一下身體的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩…煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很柔弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們這些跟外表截然相反有無限體力的傢伙可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…真的不要緊嗎？  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能不要緊  要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要叫醫生來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅決不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還真丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐昨天已經那樣努力過了  倒下也是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要這麼寵著她好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是瑪莉亞小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要生病  就不要挑春假的時候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新學期開學的時候倒下的話就能名正言順地翹課了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  比想像中的要精神多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}因為是管家和大小姐的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門去買東西  那孩子就交給你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  她昨天一天確實很努力了  倒下也是情有可原  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯…小颯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  看她用那弱弱的聲音喊著你呢  快點過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉嚨很難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想喝蘋果汁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  馬上為您準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？瑪莉亞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞小姐出門去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…克勞斯先生也出去了  要等明天才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球球和白野威也去了寵物之家作定期檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就只有我們兩個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到變成和小颯兩個人獨處了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小颯趁我生病不能動彈來推倒我的話該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後對我做這樣那樣的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道  連那種事情也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯的確是個很紳士的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是媽媽也跟我說過「男人都是披著羊皮的狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…  可是…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就回隔壁房間去了  有什麼事的話請叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確沒發生意外是好事…好歹你也要注意一下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…一個人的話很寂寞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能動彈又睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就留在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…生病的時候還是不要勉強  好好睡一覺比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就想辦法讓我入睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…想辦法讓您入睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把自己原創的搖籃曲以MikuMiku的形式唱給您聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（宅方版Miku的UmaUma？睡得著才怪！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是多此一舉嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這個  就沒有別的方法了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣興奮可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  講故事怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人入睡的經典節目不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我當成小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…算了  我就暫且忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託選個有趣一點的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說經典的話  那就是「愛麗絲夢遊仙境」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以「根絕戰爭」為目標的Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（刹那夢遊仙境？Gundam OO的NETA就不多說了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲要進行武力介入嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷了各種情節  愛麗絲她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到了不可思議的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像來到了個奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡究竟是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為突發事件而感到困惑的愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡遇到了向她搭訕的三個神秘的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀  沒見過的臉孔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那竟然是  會說話的兔子們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是引路的兔子喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要不要我把出口告訴你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯哼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbits
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲同情地說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣肉角色還真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得那麼直白！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  要想到出口的話就要通過這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個會動的地面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下的話就會被帶到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想原地不動的話就要全力奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想向前跑的話就必須要更加奮力地奔跑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將蘊含其中的社會規則毫無保留的暴露出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經典的試練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就趕去吧  愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想到出口  就在這裡全力跑起來給我們看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話音未落  愛麗絲的身影已經消失不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希  在那邊那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於平時就比常人更加努力的愛麗絲來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度已經算不上是試練了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後  單槍匹馬就打倒了眾多撲克牌士兵的愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達到了神奇王國的頂點  建立了新的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的名字叫做「合眾國日本」  大家和平地生活了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:34.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（叛逆的魯路修…）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀  可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡可喜可賀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎  一點也沒什麼值得慶祝的  根本無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好用珍藏的結局了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽下回分解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒下回了  到B-Part再繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣了？小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小颯  就沒有其它更有趣的書了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  有本「基於新粒子的發現的GN-Drive基礎理論」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？伊奧利亞那老頭是活在這個時代的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好休息才行  小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躺在床上做的已經全做了  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新刊連載都看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新作Game也都通關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個時間段也沒有動畫在播放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因為這樣  所以感冒才好不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  就算睡不著也給我躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯  我好無聊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我準備個能消磨三小時左右的有趣的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個小攝影機觀察螞蟻的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀察螞蟻有什麼好玩的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Packy啊Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺吃了Packy的話  馬上就能睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在馬上給我去買Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  只要是為了大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領結歪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你到底是怎麼了？突然說想吃Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  這比觀察螞蟻要有價值多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？居然用微型攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得會很有趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的確有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  Switch On！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子像是在追一隻搶魚的野貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在笑他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  不用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免了無意義的殺生  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被捲進麻煩事裡了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是「想去買個東西  於是來到城裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（富士台的長篇動畫“海螺小姐(サザエさん)”OP的歌詞…）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子像是忘記帶錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至於連這也和歌詞一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？咲夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說些什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  你穿著還真合適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不得不給你加工錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只做一個小時而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我忘記帶錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  回來拿一下不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  晚飯前一定將Packy給您買來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯真是讓人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉露熱茶兩杯  讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  伊澄  好可愛的女僕小姐喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？颯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澄小姐和令堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會來人這麼多的店裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從咲夜那拿到了這裡的免費券哦  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好打了一小時工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣總算能回歸正軌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再被捲進什麼不幸事件中就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亙那傢伙   有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  用我為了應付這種情況而學的讀唇術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了應付怎樣的情況而學的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前偷偷租給凪的《拜託了雙子星》DVD  趕快還回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:49.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（《おねがい★ツインズ》，中譯《拜託了雙子星》，\N《拜託了老師》的續篇。台灣代理商普威爾譯為《星空的邂逅2》）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算每集都有入浴的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但女孩子看了也不會高興的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞞著我租了那種DVD啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  還是別管這個繼續看小颯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後又過了兩小時…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人問路15次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助有麻煩的老年人23次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上因為強盜事件路被封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後碰上了那個強盜  並把他捉拿歸案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還偶然地找到了團伙的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果到最後還…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我要買Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有貨的話  我也想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是Packy這種小點心滅絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道  Packy還真有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來平時不注意社會潮流是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是Packy節！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吃Packy吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼今天突然想吃Packy了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到Packy是這麼好吃的下酒菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是運氣差到讓人想哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚為小颯做一頓牛肉火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連雛菊都在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到Packy竟然會這麼好賣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道為什麼  突然就想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯你…難不成沒買到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼變成你吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸之後又來女禍了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想玩的話  Packy什麼的就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒關係的  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得還有一個賣Packy的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創業一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小胡同裡偷偷經營著的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個只有少數人知道的幻之點心店的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還有賣剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大小姐  我一定會在晚飯前買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以請您再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之點心店嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是過期食品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…只是個點心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟讓他那麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Packy什麼的其實根本沒所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我不知為什麼也覺得想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個原因  小颯就被使喚來使喚去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有貨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？西澤同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯為什麼會在這創業一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小胡同裡偷偷經營著的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有少數人知道的幻之點心店裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該請她讓給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  說得出口嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西澤小姐也是特意跑來這創業一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小胡同裡偷偷經營著的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有少數人知道的幻之點心店來買Packy的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…為了大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能變成惡鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西…西澤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  超喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後小颯為了買Packy跑遍了周圍的市縣  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了世界盡頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得小颯他好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該叫他回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…  連通訊手段都失去了的小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會就這樣放棄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Combat Butler！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  他…準備將Packy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將Packy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將Packy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服了重重困難  終於得到了Packy呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說很明顯是仿造的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就姑且認同他的努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去準備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯的Packy  不要吃太多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  我現在就把Packy送到你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是我自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯…小颯…小颯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  小凪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  小颯他  小颯他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯出車禍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻趕往現場  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡三千院家的所有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要救小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我沒讓他去買Packy的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  晚了一點  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  這樣不行的啊  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好回房裡躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好解釋一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點被卡車撞是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為手裡拿著足球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然奇蹟般地毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如朋友般  足球救了我一命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大空翼的名言：足球是朋友）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  盡讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個…Packy嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卡車壓了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這根已經是盡了全力的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  攝影機壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是大小姐的管家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大小姐的想法了如直掌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Packy也吃到了  這下大小姐可以安心睡覺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你也是  累了的話就回房間睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我會陪在大小姐身邊直到您睡著的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是讓他買個Packy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓人擔心成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒出息的管家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且帶回來的Packy只有一根
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那根Packy是世界第一的美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就是新學期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  這是做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是新學期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微撒嬌一下  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  放開了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:22:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…  伊澄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果分到一個班的話  就請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指教什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指教什麼…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？新學期剛開學就要告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事  少主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連你也在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新學期伊始之際
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大叔的講話  太長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好聽人講話的話  會被揍的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  今天又能和大小姐一起上學了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊  難道我感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多也該咳完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去學校了哦  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼說得好像是我在裝病一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊得這麼精神  就算生病也給我上學去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
